AddressInfo.Title: University of Alabama in Huntsville - Shelby Center
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Six Clipper Creek Level 2 chargers available in the parking in front of the student services building. No permit necessary to use! Three chargers on each side of the parking lot. Dunkin Donuts, Chik-fil-A, Papa John's, and other restaurants available in student center which is within walking distance. Signage is up and you must be charging while parked here.
